  "properties": {
    "encrypted": "false",
    "display_name": "Malware Analyst",
    "long_instructions": "## Malware Analyst\r\n\r\nA **malware analyst** studies malicious software to understand how it works, how it spreads, and how to remove it.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. Chat with the malware analyst about your scenario. Figure out how the threat works and what harm it can cause.\r\n\r\n:::details [Not sure where to start?]\r\nTry using the following prompt:\r\n> I received an email from a friend with a link to download a file. I downloaded and opened the file, but instead of getting cheat codes it sent a fake email to everyone in my contacts list. Based on this scenario, how does this type of virus work and why is it harmful?\r\n\r\n:::\r\n\r\nChat with the malware analyst about **ways to prevent viruses.**\r\n\r\n:::details [Not sure where to start?]\r\nTry using the following prompt:\r\n> What are ways to prevent viruses?\r\n:::\r\n\r\n3. Chat with the malware analyst about **ways to prevent viruses using AI.**\r\n\r\n:::details [Not sure where to start?]\r\nTry out the following prompts:\r\n> - *How can AI detect new or unknown viruses before traditional antivirus software does?*\r\n> - *Can AI identify suspicious behavior on a system that might indicate a virus infection?*\r\n> - *How could AI be used to detect bugs more easily?*\r\n:::\r\n\r\n4. Chat with the malware analyst about **ways that AI can make viruses more harmful.**\r\n\r\n:::details [Not sure where to start?]\r\nTry out the following prompts:\r\n> - *How might bad actors use AI in sending viruses, and what does that mean for defenders?*\r\n> - *How does AI change the threat landscape for viruses as a cyber threat?*\r\n:::",
